<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>testingforhsosaka@163.com</span><span>（申请《健康状况声明书》及核酸检测咨询专用）</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">3、驻福冈总领馆：</span></p>
